Package: utilitybelt
Title: Collection of Utility Functions
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person(given = "Sam",
           family = "El-Kamand",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "selkamand@ccia.org.au")
Description: This package is an assortment of general-use utility functions that make life easier, particularly when working on commandline scripts. It includes functions for loading libraries silently UNLESS an error is thrown, to getting the name of a function from within that function, colorising text output, and more.
